{
  "texts": [
    "Recently it's been being adapted as a planner for decentralized MAPF (Das et al. 2016; Wang et al. 2019; Ahmed et al. 2021; Tang et al. 2020).",
    "ACO, on the other hand, is a probabilistic technique inspired by the foraging behavior of ant colonies secreting pheromone-based communication to find the shortest path to the food source.",
    "ACO can also be used to develop decentralized MAPF (Seyyedabbasi and Kiani 2020).",
    "GA is based on the evolution mechanism, the process that drives biological evolution.",
    "In GAs, genetic operators which follow the process of natural selection and genetics select candidate solutions to search for the optimal solution."
  ]
}